    This enumeration holds pairs of additional sense codes and additional sense code qualifiers. All 745 combinations relevant for direct access block devices are listed.

    Since additional sense codes and additional sense code qualifiers cannot be combined arbitrarily, a single enumeration has been chosen to represent those two fields.
